title: Astros take 2-1 series lead over Royals with 4-2 win
text:
> Top News Astros take 2-1 series lead over Royals with 4-2 win Kansas City Royals' Lorenzo Cain walks back to the dugout after striking out in the ninth inning to end the game against the Houston Astros in Game 3 of baseball's American League Division Series Sunday, Oct. 11, 2015, in Houston. The Astros won 4-2. (AP Photo/Patric Schneider)
